BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260518T091800
DTEND:20260518T115400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.048ft at 09:18\n-2.995ft at 11:54\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 NW swell mix tapers off and is down a few notches from Sunday. SSW is down
  to leftovers. The combo of swells puts average spots in the waist-chest h
 igh waves in the morning with a few larger sets\, dipping into the afterno
 on. \n\nDraining negative low tide for the dawn patrol\, then incoming tid
 e push lends a hand much of the morning. Early afternoon high tide bogs do
 wn tide sensitive spots. Light/variable AM winds expected to turn light W 
 for mostly clean conditions in town over the PM. 
END:VEVENT
