BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260521T060000
DTEND:20260521T072400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.812ft at 06:00\n-0.062ft at 07:24\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 NW energy eases further\, while S swell holds and becomes the dominant swe
 ll for most spots in town. Most breaks continue to see size in the waist t
 o chest high+ range\, while summer focal points see sets a tad larger.\n\n
 Light winds look to continue. 
END:VEVENT
